summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of Lots 1, 2, 3 and 4, Block 3, Town of Yesler Addition, and a portion of Government Lot 2 in Section 15, Township 25 North, Range 4 East, W. M., with respect to Use and Area District, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto two new sections to be numbered 2-41 and 17-24, respectively.
